title: "You Can Go In Now If You Want" (w/ Natalie Walker)

description:
Matt & Bowen welcome guest and fellow culturista Natalie Walker to the studio! The three talk shitting in plastic bags, performers who can make a meal out of a snack, bathtub acting, Disney world, and most importantly, awards season. Plus, Matt & Bow reminisce about the early days of Las Culturistas, after a tearful goodbye to HPJ.
